thread.title: Invl Technology Net Profit For 2017, Taking Into Account Revaluation Of Financial Assets, Eur 3.4 Mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: Invl Technology Net Profit For 2017, Taking Into Account Revaluation Of Financial Assets, Eur 3.4 Mln
text:
March 1 (Reuters) - INVL Technology :
* REPORTED ON WEDNESDAY NET PROFIT FOR 2017, TAKING INTO ACCOUNT A REVALUATION OF FINANCIAL ASSETS, EUR 3.4 MLN.
* EQUITY CAPITAL EUR 23.1 MLN OR EUR 1.90 PER SHARE, AT THE END OF 2017, UP 17.3 PER CENT DURING THE YEAR.
Source text : bit.ly/2GSgqEF
 (Gdynia Newsroom)
